\id 1CO - Ndendeule Bible Version
\h 1 Akakolintu
\toc1 Baluwa jhukutumbula jha Pauli kwa Akakolintu
\toc2 1 Akakolintu
\toc3 1 Akak
\mt2 Baluwa jhukutumbula jha Pauli kwa
\mt1 Akakolintu
\imt1 Ulongolelo
\ip Baluwa jhukutumbula jha Pauli jhijhandikwe na ntenga jwa Pauli pakate jha muchaka cha makome nhwano na nhwano kubhoke Yecho Kilichitu pabhelwika, mu chula jha 1:1. Jhenje ndi ikibha baluwa jhukutumbula pakate jha baluwa ibhele ya Pauli ikajhandikwe na Pauli kwa makunde gha bhando ghhighannyeketii Kilichitu gha ku Kolintu. Akajhandike baluwa jhenje pakibha atamita ku Epecho kabula jha kuhamuu kutyangila ku Kolintu, pakibha ajhahwila na kubhujha ku Makedoniya, mu chula jha 16:5-9.
\ip Baluwa jhenje ndi Pauli ajhanguu malobhe gha jhiletitwe na bhando kwa bhange, malobhe ghighalongelwa ghighateii na kikunde cha bhando chikinnyeketii Kilichitu, gwanganandela gwenio ndi mpechengano na ngongola. Muche gwa ku Kolintu ukamanyikine hake kwa ngongola, yenio lijhambu lya yakukangacha kwa kikunde cha bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu kwa mambu gheniya. Helahela baluwa jhenje jha kutumbula kwa bhando bha ku Kolintu, mu chula jha 13 ghabhii malobhe gha upalu.
\iot Ghughabhii mukitabo
\io1 Pauli abhajhambucha bhando bha ku Kolintu na innomba Chapanga kwa nhwalo gwabhe, mu chula jha 1:1-9.
\io1 Pauli ilonge malobhe gha mpechengano pakate jha likunde lilinnyeketii Kilichitu lya kwenio ku Kolintu, mu chula jha 1:10-4: 21.
\io1 Pauli ilongelela malobhe gha ngongola na kupelekana pamihalo bhene kwa bhene, mu chula jha 5-6.
\io1 Pauli ilongelela malobhe gha ipwatilila panane jha kutolelana, helahela mapwatalilo panane jha kupiya litambiko kwa inyagho na mapwatalilo panane jha kuyoka, mu chula jha 7-15.
\io1 Pauli ijhomolela kwa kukilongelela jwenio na mahengo ghake, mu chula jha 16.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nenga Napauli, jhungemitwe kubhehe natenga jwa Kilichitu Yecho kwa kupala Chapanga, na nnongo gwito Sositenesi.
\p 
\v 2 Tunyandikile mangota ma bhando bhumunyeketii Chapanga bhumii ku Kolintu, mangota nhengitwe kubhehe bhanyahinyahi mu kulombana na Kilichitu Yecho, pamonga na bhando bhoha popoha bhubhannyopa Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 3 Ninyope umbone na uteeke kuhumii kwa Chapanga Tate gwito na Bhambo Yecho Kilichitu.
\s1 Mota ya Chapanga
\p 
\v 4 Ninchenguu Chapanga kwa machiko ghoha kwa nhwalo gwino mangota mme na umbone gwake kwa ndela jha Kilichitu Yecho.
\v 5 Nhwalo, kwa kulombana na Kilichitu, mangota nnyambulile ilebhe yoha. Nnyambulile mukulonge na kumanya.
\v 6 Nhwalo malobhe gha uchakaka gha Kilichitu ghajhemite mbone nkate jhino.
\v 7 Hilu mpungokilwe jhe na hupo jhojhoha kubhoke kwa Uhuke gwa Chapanga, kongo mmii mu kunendelela Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu papala kubhonekana.
\v 8 Jwenio nakangamalicha mangota ade lichiko lya kujhomolela, nkotoka kubhonekana kubhehe na ulemo lichiko lela lya Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu.
\v 9 Chapanga ndi jwahobholeka, jwenio ankemite mangota maghumba nde na Mwana mundo Yecho Kilichitu, Bhambo gwito.
\s1 Mpechanganiko gwa bhando bhubhannyeketii Kilichitu
\p 
\v 10 Makalongo bhango, ninyopa kwa liina lya Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu, nnyilane kwa kila kilebhe chimulongela, panga mpechangano pakate jhino, mme na liwacho limo na lilobhe limo.
\v 11 Makalongo bhango, bhando bhange kubhoke munyumba jha Kuloe bhanobhalile mangota mjhangulana jhe.
\v 12 Nipala kulonge chenje, kila jhumo alonge lyake, jhumo alonge, “Nenga naningekama Pauli,” na jhonge alonge, “Nenga naningengama Apolu,” na jhonge ilonge, “Nenga naningengama Kefa,” na jhonge alonge, “Nenga naningengama Kilichitu.”
\v 13 Bho, Kilichitu apechanganike? Bho, Pauli ndi jwakabhambitwe panchalaba kwa nhwalo gwino? Bho, makabatichwe mme bhabholwa bha Pauli?
\p 
\v 14 Ninchenguu Chapanga nhwalo nikabatiche jhe mundo jhojhoha mu lilongo lino nambo Kilisipo na Gayo tugha.
\v 15 Yene mundo jhojhoha akotoka kulonge akabatichwe kwa liina lyango.
\v 16 Ngohe ngombwike! Helahela nakabatiche Sitefano na bhando bhibhakibha nkate jhake, nambo nikomboka jhe anda nikambatiche mundo jhonge.
\v 17 Kilichitu akandumite jhe nenga kubaticha, nambo andumite kwatangachii bhando Malobhe gha Mbone, changahobholela bhando bhina malango, nhwalo likakala lya kuwe kwake Kilichitu pa nchalaba kibhonekana kilebhe nacho.
\s1 Kilichitu ndi likakala na malango gha Chapanga
\p 
\v 18 Nhwalo malobhe gha kuwe kwa Yecho Kilichitu pa nchalaba ndi kilebhe cha ndindilima kwa bhala bhubhabhii mulilongo lya bhibhahobholela, nambo kwa twenga bhutughombokoka, tulibhona likakala lya Chapanga.
\v 19 Nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghalonge,
\q1 “Chahangabhana malango ghabhe kwa bhando bhubhabhii na malango,
\q1 nu kumanya kwabhe chandaghila kutale.”
\m 
\v 20 Bho, bhabhii ko, bhando bhubhabhii na malango? Bho, bhabhii ko, bhabhola bha malaghalikilo? Bhabhii ko bhina malango hake? Chapanga alangi njwe malango gha bhando bha nnema ghongo kubhehe undindilima.
\p 
\v 21 Kwa malango gha Chapanga, ihotoleka jhe bhando kummanya Chapanga kwa malango ghabhe, Chapanga akapahi kwakombola bhala bhubhajheketii kupete malobhe ghatutangachila, malobhe ghala ghughabhonekana undindilima kwa bhando bhina malango.
\v 22 Akayahude bhapala ikangacho, na Akagilike bhapala malango.
\v 23 Nambo twenga tuntangacha malobhe gha Kilichitu jwabhambitwe panchalaba. Kibhonekana kingobhahe kwa Akayahude, na undindilima kwa bhando bha ilambo henge.
\v 24 Nambo kwa bhala bhubhakemitwe na Chapanga, bhoha Akayahude na Akagilike, Kilichitu ndi likakala lya Chapanga na malango gha Chapanga.
\v 25 Nhwalo chikibhonekana undindilima kwa Chapanga, kibhii na malango kupeta malango gha mundo, na chikibhonekana kikwete jhe makakala kwa Chapanga, kibhii na makakala kuliku makakala gha bhando.
\p 
\v 26 Makalongo bhango, ngohe nkomboke pingemitwa na Chapanga, bhamahele pakate jhino mukibha jhe na malango kulengana na mawacho gha bhando, bhamahele jhe bhumukibha na likakala amu bhando bhumukibha aakolongwa.
\v 27 Nambo Chapanga akahagwile ilebhe ya pannema ibhonekane ya undindima, kupala kwapeke hone bhubhabhii na malango, Chapanga akahagwii ilebhe ileghelike kupala kwapeke hone bhala bhubhakwete makakala.
\v 28 Chapanga ahagwii ilebhe ibhonekana ipechelike na bhando na ghala ghabhonekana kilebhe nacho na yanganandela, kupala kughahangabhana ghighabhonekana na bhando kubhehe makolongwa pannema.
\v 29 Chapanga akatehi yenio kupala mundo jhojhoha akotoka kukiloka palonge jhake.
\v 30 Chapanga ndi jwanombaniche mangota na Kilichitu Yecho. Chapanga antei Kilichitu kubhehe malango ghito, kwa ndela jhake twenga tujhelanichwa na Chapanga, tubhehe bhando bha nyahinyahi na kughombokoka.
\v 31 Bhahe, ngita chighalongela Majhandiko gha Chapanga, “Jwapala kukiloka, na alokela lihengo lya Bhambo.”
\c 2
\s1 Lilobhe panane jha Yecho jwabhambitwe panchalaba
\p 
\v 1 Makalongo bhango, nenga pahikita kwino nikatumii jhe malobhe makolongwa na malango gha bhando kutangacha chile jha Chapanga.
\v 2 Nhwalo panikibha na mangota nikapahijhe kumanya chochoha nga Yecho Kilichitu kanjika, jhola jwabhambitwe panchalaba.
\v 3 Panikibha kwino nikibha leghele, nikalendime kwa kujhoghopa hake.
\v 4 Mabholo ghango na matangacho ghango nongila jhe kwa malobhe gha kuhutila bhando bhina malango, nambo ghakibha na likakala lya Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\v 5 Ndehila naha nipala kihobholelo chino kikotoka kubhehe jhe mu malango gha bhando nambo itame mu makakala gha Chapanga.
\s1 Malango gha Chapanga
\p 
\v 6 Nambo tutangacha malobhe gha malango kwa bhala bhubhakomii muhuke, nambo malango ghanga chi gha pamba pannema, hilu chi gha malango gha ilongoche bha nnema ghongo bhubhabhii mu lilongo lya kuhobhelela.
\v 7 Tutangacha malango gha Chapanga ghighaihitwe, Chapanga akahagwii kabula jha nnema kupanganwa kwa nhwalo gwa ung'alicho gwito.
\v 8 Bhabhijhe akakolongwa bha nnema ghongo bhubhamanya malango ghanga. Ngaumanya bhakoto kummamba pa nchalaba Bhambo jwa ung'alicho.
\v 9 Nambo ngita chighalonge Majhandiko gha Chapanga,
\q1 “Mambu ghala liho inahwaijhe kulola, na lichikilo inawahijhe kujhoha,
\q1 mambu gha bhando ahwachite jhe mu mwojho,
\q1 gheniya ndi Chapanga aghabhekite kwa bhala bhubhampahile.”
\m 
\v 10 Gheniya ndi mambu Chapanga akatujhogholile kwa ndela jha Uhuke gwa Chapanga. Nhwalo Uhuke gwa Chapanga alingukiya kila kilebhe ade mambu gha nkate jha Chapanga.
\v 11 Ghane jwahotola kumanya mambu gha nkate jha mundo nga uhuke gwake mundo jwenio? Helahela abhii jhe jwamanya mambu gha Chapanga nga Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\v 12 Bhahe, twenga tupokiijhe uhuke gwa nnema, nambo tupokii Uhuke ghuhumita kwa Chapanga kupala kumanya ghala ghatupekei jhajhe Chapanga.
\p 
\v 13 Bhahe, twenga tubhola chi kwa malobhe kwa malango gha bhando bhahoto kubhola, nambo tulonge panane jha mambu ghanga kwa malobhe gha Uhuke gwa Chapanga ibhola, tuchimulila ilebhe ya Kihuke gwa Chapanga kwa bhando bhubhabhii na Kihuke.
\v 14 Mundo jwangabhehe na Uhuke gwa Chapanga ahoto jhe kughamanya mambu ghala ghighahumita kwa Chapanga, nhwalo ghibhonekana undindima kwa jwenio na amanyita jhe, nhwalo ghamanyikina kwa kutangatilwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\v 15 Nambo mundo jwakwete Uhuke gwa Chapanga, ahoto kughamanya ghoha, na abhii jhe jhonge jwahoto kunhadabhula.
\v 16 Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghalonge,
\q1 “Ghane jwahoto kumanya malango gha Bhambo?
\q1 Ghane jwahoto kunnongocha Bhambo?”
\m Nambo twenga tuwacha ngita Kilichitu chiihwacha.
\c 3
\s1 Lihengo lya bhabhola
\p 
\v 1 Makalongo bhango, nenga nikahotwii jhe kulonge na mangota anda nilonge na bhando bhubhakwete Uhuke gwa Chapanga. Nipalwa kulonge na mangota anda bhando bha nnema, ngita yana ilemba mu kihobholelo cha Kilichitu.
\v 2 Nipekii mabhele, na chi chakulyegha kijhundupaho, nhwalo ngauhotwii jhe kulyegha. Helahela ngohe mihoto jhe kulyegha.
\v 3 Nhwalo mangota mwamela mitama ngita bhando bha kiyegha chibhatama. Bho, chakaka jhe kubhehe ubhii wiho na bhulo pakate jhino? Mambu ghanga ghalangii chakaka kubhehe mangota ndi bhando bha nnema, mitama ngita bhando bha nnema chibhatama.
\v 4 Jhumo gwino palongela, “Nenga ninkengama Pauli,” na jhonge, “Nenga ninkengama Apolu” Bho, muhenga jhe ngita chibhahenga bhando bha nnema?
\p 
\v 5 Apolu ndi ghane? Na Pauli ndi ghane? Twenga ndi akatumiche bha Chapanga kupete lihengo lito mangota nkwete kihobholelo, na kila mundo ahenga lihengo lyapatite na Bhambo.
\v 6 Nenga nikamichite mbejho, Apolu ajhitilile mache, nambo jwamelecha mbejho ndi Chapanga.
\v 7 Jwamicha mbejho na jhola jwajhitilila mache, kilebhe nacho nambo Chapanga kanjika ndi nkolongwa jwaitenda imele.
\v 8 Mundo jhola jwamichite mbejho na jhola jwajhitilila mache bhoha bhahengite kilebhe chimo, nambo Chapanga channepa malepo kila mundo kwa lihengo lyake.
\v 9 Nhwalo twenga tuhenga mahengo pamonga na Chapanga, na mangota ndi nng'onda gwa Chapanga.
\p Mangota ndi nyumba jha Chapanga.
\v 10 Kwa utangatilo gwa umbone gwa Chapanga, nimekite nchinge ngita mundo jwahoto kuchenga mbone, na mundo jhonge kuchenga panane jhake. Nambo kila mundo jwapala kuchenga akilolekiye papala kuchenga panane jhake.
\v 11 Abhii jhe mundo jhonge jwahoto kubheka nchinge ghonge kuliku ghola ghubhekitwe, ndi Yecho Kilichitu.
\v 12 Panane jha nchinge gwenio, mundo jhumo jwahoto kuchenga kwa chaabo, amu kuchenga kwa feza amu kuchenga kwa maghanga gha mbijha ngolongwa, amu kuchenga kwa mikongo, amu kuchenga kwa mahamba amu manyahe.
\v 13 Kwa ndela jhojhoha jhambone jha lihengo lya kila mundo chilibhonekana hotu, mu machiko ghala gha Kilichitu. Nhwalo lichiko lyenio mwotu chaupema kila lihengo lya mundo, na mwotu gwenio naujhigha ngita lyambone.
\v 14 Anda lihengo lya mundo jwenio litinike jhe pamwotu, mundo jwenio chapata hupo,
\v 15 nambo anda chachengite kitinike, bhahe, mundo jwenio najhambulii jhe kilebhe, nambo jwenio chakombwilwe anda aholwite mu mwotu.
\p 
\v 16 Bho, mu manyajhe mangota ndi Nyumba jha Chapanga, na Uhuke gwa Chapanga atama nkate jhino?
\v 17 Bhahe, mundo jwahangabhana Nyumba jha Chapanga, Chapanga chahangabhana mundo jwenio. Nhwalo Nyumba jha Chapanga ndi nyahinyahi, na nyumba jhene ndi mangota mabhene.
\p 
\v 18 Nkoto kukikolowa mabhene! Mundo jhojhoha pakate jhino jwawacha kubhehe jhuna malango gha pannema, mbaha kubhonekana lindindilima kupala kubhehe na malango chakaka.
\v 19 Nhwalo, malango gha nnema ghongo ndi undindima palonge jha Chapanga. Helahela Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghalonge, “Chapanga ajhakwakamula bhubhabhii na malango mukukalamuka kwabhe.”
\v 20 Kabhele Majhandiko ghange ghalonge, “Bhambo amanya kubhehe mawacho gha bhala bhubhabhii na malango kuchata jhe.”
\v 21 Bhahe, mundo nkotoka kukilokela ghala ghibhahenga bhando. Nhwalo kila kilebhe ndi chino.
\v 22 Abhe Pauli amu abhe Apolu amu Kefa, amu nnema amu ughome amu kuwe, mambu gha chaa jhenje amu ghala ghighapala kuhika palonge, nhwalo ghoha ndi ghino.
\v 23 Nambo mangota ndi bhando bha Kilichitu, na jwenio Kilichitu ndi jwa Chapanga.
\c 4
\s1 Akatenga bha Kilichitu
\p 
\v 1 Kila mundo amanye kubhehe twenga ndi akatumiche bha Kilichitu, tupilwe chile jha Chapanga.
\v 2 Chikipalwa kuhenga kwa mundo jhojhoha jhola jwahengita lihengo lende ndi kubhehe jhuna kihobholelo.
\v 3 Kwa nenga kilebhe jhe kuhadabulwa na mangota, amu na udamo gwa pannema, hilu nikihadabula jhe namwene.
\v 4 Ku mwojho gwango ngwete jhe matakalilo kwa lijhambu lyolyoha, nambo ilangii jhe ngwete jhe jwangokolekeya. Bhambo ndi jwahoto kuhadabula.
\v 5 Bhahe, nkotoka kunhadabhula mundo kabula jha lichaa lyake, muneke ade Bhambo papakuhika. Jwenio chahumbula mambu ghoha ghughabhii mulubhendo, na kubheka hotu ghughabhii umiojho jha bhando. Peniya kila mundo chapata ulumbililo ghutopela kubhoke kwa Chapanga.
\p 
\v 6 Makalongo bhango, nintumii Apolu na nenga namwene nhwalo kupete nnandanikiho ghongo mukibhole malobhe ghanga, “Nkamule ghughabhii mu majhandiko ghango.” Nkotoka kukilokela kwa mundo jhumo na kunpucha jhonge.
\v 7 Ghane jwantehi mwenga kubhehe makolongwa kuliku bhange? Bho, Chapanga ammanyite jhe ilebhe yunkwete? Bho, anda mpatite nike chimukilokela anda mpokii jhe?
\p 
\v 8 Bho, ngohe mpatite yoha imuipala? Bho, ngohe nkwete ilebhe mbwe? Mmii akanahota panga twenga! Chakaka, nipala mme akanahota ngita twenga mukulongocha pamonga na mangota.
\v 9 Niwacha Chapanga atutehi twenga twakatenga bha bhando bha pahe, ngita bhando bhubhahadabwilwe kuwe, nhwalo tubhii anda unyagho palonge jha nnema ghoha, palonge jha akatumiche bha kunane kwa Chapanga na bhando.
\v 10 Twenga ndi akamandindilima nhwalo gwa kuntumikila Kilichitu, nambo mangota nkwete malango mu kulombana na Kilichitu! Tubhonekana bhando bhubhabhii leghele! Nambo mangota nkwete makakala! Mangota mitopela! Nambo twenga tubhonekana kupecheleka!
\v 11 Ade ngoheno, twenga tukwete njala na nyota, tukwetejhe ngobho, tutyalwa, ngwetejhe pakutama.
\v 12 Kabhele tubhikulagha hake kuhenga lihengo kwa mabhoko ghito twabhete. Putuligwa, twenga twajhopela mota, putung'ahika, twenga tuhimbalila,
\v 13 Putuligwa twenga tujhangula mbone. Ade ngoheno tubhonekana ngita luku lwa nnema, na kwa kila mundo tubhonekana uchapo!
\p 
\v 14 Nijhandika ndeka mambu ghanga kupala kwapeke hone, nambo nibhola ngita yana yango inipahile.
\v 15 Ata ngabhehe akayaya elufo kome mu kulombana na Kilichitu, nambo tate gwino ndi jhumo, nhwalo mu kulombana na Yecho Kilichitu nenga ndi tate gwino jwa kunnetela Malobhe gha Mbone.
\v 16 Ngohe, nipembelekeya chonde, nkengame nnandanikiho gwango.
\v 17 Kwa kuntangatila nintuma Timocheyo kwino. Jwenio ndi mwana gwango mu kulombana na Bhambo Yecho Kilichitu, jhunimpala na jwahobholeka. Jwenio nankombocha ndela jhiniikengama nenga mu kulombana na Kilichitu. Ndela jhibhola kila chehemo kwa bhando bhoha bhubhannyeketii Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 18 Bhando bhange pakate jhino bhatumbwile kuloka na kulonge nahikajhe kabhele kwino.
\v 19 Nambo, anda Bhambo apahile, chahika kwino kajhombe, peniya ndi chanikinolela namwete chi chela chimilonge majhito bhibhaloka, nambo makakala ghughabhehe nako.
\v 20 Nhwalo unahota nkolongwa gwa Chapanga chi malobhe tugha, nambo ndi likakala.
\v 21 Bho, kilebhe ghane chikinhalalila? Bho, hike kwino nayato amu hike na mwojho gwa upalo na utokomalo?
\c 5
\s1 Mwibhambale ngongola
\p 
\v 1 Ghabhii malobhe gha uchakaka kubhehe bhabhii akatenda ngongola pakate jhino, kabhele ngongola yenio inapitila jhe hilu kwa bhando bhangaummanya Chapanga. Nobholilwe kubhehe jhumo gwino igholoka na mwikeghe jwa tate mundo!
\v 2 Nauhotola bhole kuloka? Mbaha kwino kubhehe ngolongondi, na mundo jwahenga mambu gheniya abhengwa pakate jhino.
\v 3 Na nenga, kiyegha mii kutale na mangota, nambo kiuhuke tubhii pamonga, anda mmi pakate jhino ninhadabwii njwe kwa liina lya Bhambo Yecho mundo jwenio jwahengite mambu gheniya gha hone.
\v 4 Pumukonganika pamonga, na nenga mmii na mangota mu uhuke gwango, na likakala lya Bhambo gwito Yecho ibhii peniya,
\v 5 mundo jwenio munkamuye kwa Limbembela kupala yegha jhake ihangalabhanwe na uhuke gwake ukombolelwe lichiko lela Bhambo papakuhika kwahadabuu bhando.
\p 
\v 6 Kuloka kwino kuchata jhe! Bho, umanyitii jhe kubhehe kimela chandina kituta libuluma lya ukobha?
\v 7 Mukijhelebhuhe kwa kuileka ngedule gha makacho jha uhakaho na mme mukumuku. Peniya nanandana na libuluma liyono lyangabhekwa ngedule. Ngita chimupalwa kubhehe. Nhwalo, Kilichitu ndi jwabhii Pachaka abhohitwe kubhehe litambiko.
\v 8 Bhahe, tuhenge unyagho gwenio gwa Pachaka, chi kwa libumunda lya makacho, kimela cha ulemo na ubhoho. Nambo kwa libumunda lyangalekelwa ngedule, ndi mwojho gwambone na uchakaka.
\p 
\v 9 Nikanyandikile mu baluwa jhango jhenge, nkoto kuhangalwana nako bhibhatenda ngongola.
\v 10 Nilonge jhe kubhehe nkoto kuhangalwa nabho bhando bhangaummanya Chapanga, akatenda ngongola na bhubhapoka ilebhe na bhubhajhima na bhubhalongela uwange na bhubhaijhinamii inyagho. Nhwalo, kupala kwabhambala bheniya ndi ipalwa kubhoka pamba pannema!
\v 11 Nambo ngohe ninyandikila nkoto kuhangalwanwa na mundo jhojhoha jwalonge anyeketela Kilichitu kone ndi ntenda ngongola na nnyime, ajhinamii inyagho na jhuna maligho na jwalobhela na jwapoka ilebhe. Mundongita jwenio nkoto kulye nako.
\p 
\v 12 Bho, ndi lihengo lyango kwahadabhula bhando bhubhabhii panja jha bhubhannyeketii Kilichitu? Bho, mangota mipalwa ndeka kwahadabhula bhando bhubhabhii pakate jhino mabhene?
\v 13 Nambo Chapanga jwenio nabhahadabula bhando bheniya bhibhabhii panja jha bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu, ngita Majhandiko gha Chapanga chighalonge, “Mabhenge kutale bheniya bhibhatenda ubhoho pakate jhino.”
\c 6
\s1 Kutakalilana kwa akalongo bhubhajheketii Kilichitu
\p 
\v 1 Mundo anda abulana na nnyake, naibhabho jhumo kuntakalila pa Bwalo jha bhando bhangaummanya Chapanga kuneka kuntakalila kwa bhando bha Chapanga?
\v 2 Bho, mmanyii jhe kubhehe bhando bha Chapanga chibhauhadabula nnema? Anda mangota uhoto kunhadabula nnema, nhwalo ghane mihoto jhe kuhadabula kwa mambu machokomachoko?
\v 3 Bho, mmanyii jhe kubhehe, mangota chamwahadabula akatumiche bha kunane kwa Chapanga? Bhahe, mangota mihoto kuhadabula kuchocha mambu gha ughome ghongo.
\v 4 Pumibhehe na bhulo, bho, mwakema jhe bhando bhangabhehe na ukindendeke kwa bhando bhangannyeketii Kilichitu bhanhadabule? Bho, akajhomola mihalo ndi bhando bhangabhehe na ukindendeke kwa bhando bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu?
\v 5 Nilonge naha mbala nkole hone mabhene! Bho, abhii jhe jhumo pakate jhino jwakwete malango kuhoto kujhomola mihalo pakate jha bhubhannyeketii Kilichitu?
\v 6 Nambo mundo jwanyeketii Kilichitu ajhakunneta pa bwalo na kwaleka bhando bhangaummanya Chapanga bhahadabule!
\p 
\v 7 Ibhonekana kutakalilana mabhene kwa mabhene pa bwalo ilangii nnepelile. Bho, kilebhe chambone jhe kwino kuhimbalila ghanganandela? Bho, chambone jhe kwino kupokwa ilebhe hino?
\v 8 Nambo mangota ndi mwatendela ghanganandela na kwapoka, kabhele, gheniya mwatendela bhajhino bhibhanyeketii Kilichitu!
\v 9 Bho, mmanyite jhe kubhehe bhando bhubhahenga ghanganandela nabhabhujhii jhe unahota nkolongwa gwa Chapanga? Mwangakolohana! Bhando bhubhahenga ngongola, bhubhajhinamii inyagho, amu bhubhagholoka na akanalome bhajhabhe,
\v 10 wihe na bhibhapala ilebhe mbwe na bhubhalobhela ughembe na bhubhang'wenya, bhubhakopekeya bhange na bhubhaligha, bheniya bhoha chibhabhujhii jhe unahota nkolongwa gwa Chapanga.
\v 11 Bhange pakate jhino mukibha ngita bhando bheniya. Nambo ngoheno nnekekiwe uhakaho gwino, mmekitwe kubhehe mwa nyahinyahi, na kubhehe mmihobholeka palonge jha Chapanga kwa liina lya Bhambo Yecho Kilichitu na kwa Uhuke gwa Chapanga gwito.
\s1 Yegha jhino inombe Chapanga
\p 
\v 12 Mundo ahoto kulonge, “Kila kilebhe kijhekitelwa kwa nenga.” Telatela, nambo chi kila kilebhe chambone kwa nenga. Nijheketela kubhehe nihoto kulongocha kila kilebhe nambo nipala jhe kubhehe napungwa kwa kilebhe chochoha.
\v 13 Mihoto kulonge, “Chakulyegha ndi kwa nhwalo gwa lutumbo, na lutumbo ndi kwa nhwalo gwa chakulyegha.” Nambo Chapanga chahangabhana yoha. Yegha jha mundo chi kwa nhwalo gwa ngongola nambo kwa nhwalo gwa Bhambo, na Bhambo ndi kwa nhwalo jha yegha.
\v 14 Chapanga jwayokiche Bhambo kubhoke mukuwegha, natuyokicha na twenga helahela kwa likakala lyake.
\p 
\v 15 Bho, mmanyitii jhe yegha hino ndi ihungo ya Kilichitu? Bho, miwacha nihoto kutola chehemo jha yegha jha Kilichitu na kuitenda kubhehe chehemo jha yegha jha mundo jwatenda ngongola? Nahi jhe!
\v 16 Bho, umanyite jhe, jwalombana na mwikeghe jwatenda ngongola bhabhii yegha jhimo? Ngita chijhandikwe mu Majhandiko gha Chapanga, “Na bheniya bhabhele nabhabha yegha jhimo.”
\v 17 Nambo jhola jwalombana na Bhambo bhabhehe pamonga ki Uhuke.
\p 
\v 18 Mibhambale ngongola. Uhakaho ghoha ghonge ghuhengwa panja jha yegha, nambo jwahenga ngongola ahutende uhakaho yegha jhake jwenio.
\v 19 Bho, mmanyitii jhe kubhehe yegha hino ndi Nyumba jha Uhuke gwa Chapanga jwabhii nkate jhino, jhola mumpokii kubhoke kwa Chapanga? Bhahe, mangota chi gwino mabhene.
\v 20 Nhemelilwe kwa bei ngolongwa. Ngoheno, munnombe Chapanga kwa yegha jhino.
\c 7
\s1 Machwale gha kutolela
\p 
\v 1 Kwa nhwalo gwa ghala ghunyandike.
\p Mbaha munalome akoto kutolela.
\v 2 Nambo kwa nhwalo gwa kubhambala ngongola, mbaha kila munalome abhehe na nhwana mundo, na kila mwikeghe abhehe na ungana mundo.
\v 3 Munalome ahenge ghighapalwa kuhenga kwa nhwana mundo, na jwenio nhwana mundo ahenge ghighapalwa kuhenga kwa ungana mundo.
\v 4 Nhwana mundo akwete jhe kindendeke panane jha yegha jhake, nambo ungana mundo akwete, helahela na jwenio munalome, akwete jhe kindendeke panane jha yegha jhake, nambo nhwana mundo akwete.
\v 5 Kila mundo anganyima jhe nnyake, nambo anda nnyiline ntende pandina tugha, kupala nngongela kwa nhwalo gwa kunnyopa Chapanga. Peniya kila mundo amujhile nnyake kabhele, kupala kulibhambala Limbembela kwa nhwalo jha kubhehe gwangakamilika.
\p 
\v 6 Ghanga nilonge nenga, chi malaghalikilo, nipala ntame maha.
\v 7 Nikapahile bhando bhoha bhabhehe ngita nenga, nambo kila mundo jhumo akwete kitoi chake kuhumii kwa Chapanga, jhumo kitoi chenje na jhonge chela.
\p 
\v 8 Nambo kwa bhala bhangatolela amu bhibhatolile amu mapwela, nenga nilonge naha yamaha kujhendelela kutama uholo ngita nenga.
\v 9 Nambo anda mundo ahoto jhe kuhimbilila, atolele, amu atolelwe mbaha kutolela amu kutolelwa kuliku kupala ngongola.
\p 
\v 10 Kwa bhala bhubhatolile na bhubhatolilwe napela lilaghalikilo lende, chi lilaghalikilo lyango, nambo ndi lya Bhambo, mwikeghe akoto kunneka ungana mundo.
\v 11 Nambo anda atei yenio, bhahe atame uholo, amu ajhelane nako ungana mundo. Helahela munalome akoto kunneka nhwana mundo.
\p 
\v 12 Kwa bhando bhange, ne nilonge naha, nambo malobhe ghanga ghahumitii jhe kwa Bhambo. Anda munalome akwete nhwana mundo jwanganyekete Kilichitu, na jwenio nhwana mundo ajheketile kujhendelela kutama na ungana mundo, munalome akotoka kunneka nhwana mundo.
\v 13 Anda mwikeghe akwete munalome jwanganyeketela Kilichitu, na jwenio ungana mundo ajheketile kujhendelela kutama na nhwana mundo, bhahe, mwikeghe jwenio akotoka kunneka ungana mundo.
\v 14 Kwa nhwalo munalome jwangannyeketela Kilichitu napokelelwa na Chapanga kwa kulombana na nhwana mundo. Na mwikeghe jhola jwangannyeketela Kilichitu, Chapanga napokelelwa na Chapanga kwa kulombana na ungana mundo. Anda nahijhe yana yabhe ngaibhii ngita yana yangaummanya Chapanga, nambo ngohe chakaka bheniya ndi yana ya Chapanga.
\v 15 Anda mundo jwannyeketela Kilichitu apala kunneka nnyake jwanyeketela Kilichitu bhahe anneke tugha. Munalome amu mwikeghe jwannyeketela Kilichitu ahibhilikii jhe kutenda yenio. Chapanga atukemite twenga tutame kwa uteeke.
\v 16 Mwe makeghe jhumujheketii Kilichitu, naumanya bho, anda namunkombola jhe ungana gwino? Amu mwenga manalome jhumujheketile Kilichitu naumanya bho namunkombola jhe nhwana gwino?
\s1 Ntame ngita chankemitwe na Chapanga
\p 
\v 17 Kila mundo atame tela na kitoi chapekiwe na Bhambo, na ngita akemitwe na Chapanga. Lyenio ndi lilaghalikio lyango kwa bhando bhubhannyeketii Kilichitu.
\v 18 Anda mundo akemitwe na Chapanga kongo jwangajhingii jando, bhahe akotoka kukikopokeya ajhingii jhe jando. Anda mundo pakemitwa ajhingii jhe jando, bhahe akotoka kujhingii jando.
\v 19 Nhwalo kujhingii jando amu changajhingii jando kilebhenacho, kilebhe kikolongwa ndi kukamula lilaghalikilo lya Chapanga.
\v 20 Bhahe, kila mundo na ahighilike ngita chakibha pakemitwa na Chapanga.
\v 21 Bho, mwenga pukemitwa na Chapanga mukibha jhe mmanda? Tela, nkotoka kupwelela, nambo anda mpatite pwache nhenge.
\v 22 Nhwalo jwenio jwakemitwa na Bhambo pakibha mmanda, jwenio jwalekekilwe na Bhambo. Helahela jwakemitwa kongo mmanda jhe, jwenio nabhaha mmanda jwa Kilichitu.
\v 23 Chapanga aunhemile mangota kwa mbijha jhamahele, nkotoka kubhehe akabhanda bha bhando.
\v 24 Makalongo bhango, kila mundo ajhendelele kutama na Chapanga, nhwalo Chapanga abhii pamonga na twenga.
\s1 Malobhe gha bhando bhangatolela na mapwela
\p 
\v 25 Ngohe kwa malobhe gha bhala bhubhatolile na bhangatolelwa, ngwete jhe lilaghalikio kuhumii kwa Bhambo, nambo nenga nilonge ghanga kwa kiya jha Bhambo nitope kuhobholeka.
\p 
\v 26 Chinilola nenga mang'ahiko ghughahika, mbaha ahighilike ngita chakibha.
\v 27 Bho, ntolile? Bhahe, mangalogwa jhe kunneka. Bho, ntolii jhe? Mangalogwa jhe kutolela.
\v 28 Nambo anda ntolile, naibhaha uhengite jhe uhakaho, anda nchikana atolilwe, ahengite jhe uhakaho, nambo bhala bhibhatola chibhapata mang'ahiko ghamahele mu ughome ghongo, na nenga nipala gheniya ghamambale mangota.
\p 
\v 29 Nambo makalongo bhango, mbala kulonge naha, machiko ghahighilike ghandina. Kutumbula ngoheno bhala bhibhatolile na bhatame ngita bhala bhangatolela,
\v 30 na bhubhalela bhabhehe anda bhangalela, na bhala bhibhaheka bhabhehe ngita bhangahangana. Na bhala bhibhahemela, ilebhe yenio ibhehe ngita yabhe jhe.
\v 31 Na bhubhabhii mukukakalakana kupalaha ilebhe ya pannema pano bhabha ngita bhando bhangakakalakana. Nhwalo nnema ghongo anda tumanye utenda kupeta.
\p 
\v 32 Nambo mbala mangota ntame changa kiholo. Mundo jwangatolela akakalakana lihengo lya Bhambo, kone ajhigha kunhalalicha Bhambo.
\v 33 Nambo munalome jwatolile akakalakana mambu gha nnema, anhalaliche nhwana mundo,
\v 34 ahutilwa na ilebhe ibhele. Mwikeghe jwangatolelwa ukakalakana na mambu gha Bhambo kupala abhehe nyahinyahi yegha na uhuke kwa Bhambo. Nambo jhola jwatolilwe ukakalakana na mambu gha nnema, kwa kunhalalila ungana mundo.
\p 
\v 35 Nilonge naha nipala kuntangatila mangota, nipala jhe kuhibhilikiya kwa chochoha, nambo ntame ngita chiipalwa na kukibhoha mabhene mu mahengo gha Bhambo changahutilwa na mambu ghange.
\p 
\v 36 Anda mundo alola ahenga mbone jhe kuntolela jhe mwikeghe jwannepii inyaghabhule, anda kuhimbilila chepa mbaha atole, anda antolile mwikeghe jwenio ahenga jhe uhakaho.
\v 37 Anda munalome alola tela kutama changatolela na ahoto kuhimbalila, mmanya kubhehe ahenga mbone kutama changa tolela jwenio nchikana.
\v 38 Jhola jwapala kutolela mwikeghe ahenga mbone, na jhola jwangatolela ahenga mbone hake.
\p 
\v 39 Mwikeghe jwatolilwe apungitwe na ungana mundo anda abhii ughome. Nambo anda ungana mundo awile, bhahe mwikeghe jwenio ahoto kutolelwa na mwanalome jhonge jwampala, nambo abhehe jwanhobhelela Kilichitu.
\v 40 Nambo panola nenga, mwikeghe jwenio nabhaha na luhangano hake anda ahighilike changatolelwa. Gheniya nilola nenga pange ngwete Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\c 8
\s1 Yakulyegha itambikilwe mahoka
\p 
\v 1 Ngohe kwa nhwalo gwa yakulyegha ikatambikilwe mahoka.
\p Tumanya kubhehe twenga twabhoha ilebhe henge, nambo kumanya kwenio kwabheka bhando kukiloka, nambo upalo uchenga.
\v 2 Jwawacha kubhehe amanya kilebhe, chakaka amela amanyite jhe chochoha anda chiipala kumanya.
\v 3 Nambo mundo jwampahi Chapanga, jwenio amanyikine na jwenio.
\p 
\v 4 Kwa gheniya, panane jha kulyegha itambikilwe mahoka, tumanya chakaka kubhehe inyagho kilebhenacho pannema, tumanya Chapanga ndi jhumo tugha.
\v 5 Ata bhakabhii bheniya bhibhakemwa inyagho pannema amu kunane kwa Chapanga, ata bhakabhii inyagho na akanahota bhamahele,
\v 6 kwito abhii Chapanga jhumo tugha, Tate, jwapangine ilebhe yoha, kwa nhwalo gwake twenga tutama. Helahela abhii Bhambo jhumo tugha, jwenio ndi Yecho Kilichitu, kwa kupete kwa jwenio ilebhe yoha ipanginwe, na twenga tutama kwa kupete jwenio.
\p 
\v 7 Nambo, chi kila mundo jwamanya uchakaka ghongo. Bhando bhange bhayobhalile hake mahoka, ade deleno pubhalyegha yakulyegha itambikilwe mahoka uhobholela njwe mumiojho jhabhe kubhehe ipihitwe yakula yenio ya mahoka. Kwa uhotolo gwa kuhaghu ghambone na ghanganandela ukwetii jhe likakala bhahola yakulye yenio yatenda bhakota kujheketelwa palonge jha Chapanga.
\v 8 Nambo chakulye kihoto jhe kutubheka pahina na Chapanga. Anda tulekite kulyegha kibhii jhe chikipongoka, anda tulyegha kibhii jhe chikijhonjekeka.
\p 
\v 9 Nambo mukilolekeye, pumulekekewa kuhenga ilebhe, nkoto kwatenda bhubhabhii na kihobholelo chandina bhatende uhakaho.
\v 10 Nhwalo, mundo jwabhii na uhotolo gwandina gwa kuhaghula lyambone na libhoho, anda amwene mangota bhakwete kihobholelo kikolongwa mulyegha yakulya yenio nkate mwa nyumba jha inyagho, bho, chabhe jhe na mwojho gwa kulyegha yakulyegha itambikilwe mahoka?
\v 11 Ngohe, jwenio nnongo gwino jwabhii na uhotolo gwandina gwa kumanya lyamaha na libhoho, jhojho jwenio Kilichitu akawile kwa nhwalo gwake chahobhelela ndeka kwa nhwalo gwa kumanya kwino.
\v 12 Anda uhenga mambu gheniya kwa ajhino bhubhajheketii Kilichitu, na kuikocholana uhotolo ileghelike kwa kuhaghuu lyamaha na libhoho, mmanye uhenga uhakaho kwa Kilichitu.
\v 13 Anda chakulye chinilyegha kintenda nnongo gwango ahenge uhakaho, nilyejhe nyama kabhele, ngoto kuntenda nnongo gwango agwe muhakaho.
\c 9
\s1 Lihengo lya akatenga na ghibhapalwa kupelwa
\p 
\v 1 Bho, ne nekekiwe jhe? Bho, ne natenga jhe? Bho, nenga nimwe jhe Yecho Bhambo gwito? Bho, mangota lihengo lyango jhe kwa kulombana na Bhambo?
\v 2 Ata ikabhii kwa bhando bhange ne natenga jhe, nambo kwino mangota nenga ndi natenga. Mangota ndi mulangiya utenga gwango kwa nhwalo gwa kulombana kwino na Bhambo.
\p 
\v 3 Naha chinikikengelela kwa bhando bhubhangonya,
\v 4 bho, tupalwa ndeka kupelwa chakulye na chakunywegha kwa nhwalo gwa lihengo lito?
\v 5 Bho, tukwete jhe ukindendeke gwa kutolela mwikeghe jwahobholela Kilichitu mukutyanga, ngita chibhahenga akatenga bhange, akalongo bhake Bhambo, na Kefa?
\v 6 Amu ndi nenga na Banaba tugha tupalwa kupata ilebhe hito kwa kuhenga lihengo?
\v 7 Bho, nkomana ngondo ghane jwalepa mbijha kwa lihengo lyake? Bho, nnema ghane jwangalyegha uhoe gwa nng'onda gwake gwa chambalau? Bho, nnucha ghane jwaikoleka jwanganywegha mabhele gha inyama yake?
\p 
\v 8 Bho, nilonge malobhe ghanga kwa kimundo tugha? Bho, lilaghalikilo lya Mucha ilongela jhe naha?
\v 9 Nhwalo ijhandikwe mu lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, “Nkotoka kuntabha nnomo ng'ombi pabula mponga.” Bho, ibhii na mana Chapanga ilongelela ng'ombi?
\v 10 Bho, palongela gheniya alongii jhe panane jha malobhe ghito? Chakaka ghanga ghajhandikwe kwa nhwalo gwito, nhwalo jhola jwalema na jhola jwahuna, bhoha bhihobholela kupata mahuno.
\v 11 Anda twenga tumichita mbejho jha kiuhuke pakate jhino, bho, kilebhe kikolongwa twenga kupata ghitupala kuhumii kwino?
\v 12 Anda bhando bhange bhipalwa kupata gheniya kubhoke kwino, bho, twenga tupalwa jhe kupata kuliku bhene?
\p Nambo, twenga tuntumii jhe ukindendeke gwenio. Tuhimbilila mu kila kilebhe kupala Lilobhe lya Mbone lya Kilichitu likotoka kubhujha unyuma.
\v 13 Bho, umanyingine jhe kubhehe bhubhahenga lihengo mu Nyumba jha Chapanga bhipata yakulegha mwenio, na bhubhabheka litambiko pakichangwale bhipata kilebhe mwenio mu litambiko?
\v 14 Helahela Bhambo akalaghalikiye naha, bhala bhibhatangachii bhando Lilobhe lya Mbone bhapate ilebhe yabhe ibhaipala kubhoke mwenio.
\p 
\v 15 Nambo nikajhopite jhe hilu kilebhe chimo. Amu nikajhandike ndeka kupala undendele gheniya. Kwa nenga mbaha kuwegha kuliku kuntenda mundo anole anda nenga nikiloka jhajhe.
\v 16 Anda nenga nitangacha Malobhe gha Mbone, chenie kilebhe jhe cha kukiloka. Lyenio ndi lihengo limpekiwe. Chanola choto anda natangachii jhe bhando Lilobhe lya Mbone!
\v 17 Anda nihenga lihengo lende kwa kupala namwete, ngahobholile kulepwa, nambo anda nenga nipalwa kuhenga lihengo lende, ilangii kubhehe Chapanga ambekii nenga kuhenga lende.
\v 18 Bho, malepo ghango kilebhe ghane? Panatangachii bhando nipala jhe kulepwa chochoha, nijhopa jhe malepo kwa lihengo lya kutangacha Lilobhe lya Mbone.
\p 
\v 19 Nenga nabhanda jhe bha mundo jhojhoha. Nikibhekite nabhanda kwa kila mundo nhwalo kunnete Kilichitu bhando bha mahele.
\v 20 Punikibha kwa Akayahude ndamita ngita Akayahude kupala kwapata Akayahude, pamonga na nenga kubhehe pahe jha lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, nambo nikibha ngita pahe jha lilaghalikilo lyenio, kupala kwapata bheniya bhubhabhii pahe jha lilaghalikilo lya Mucha.
\v 21 Punikibha na bhando bhangalongochwa na lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, nikibha ngita bheniya ngita ngwetejhe lilaghalikilo, kupala kwapata bhala bhangabhehe na lilaghalikilo lya Mucha. Kulonge yenio nenga anda nikengama jhe lilaghalikilo lya Chapanga, nhwalo mbungwitwe na lilaghalikilo lya Kilichitu.
\v 22 Punikibha na bhando bhala bhubhabhii leghele nikatamite helahela ngita chibhabhii bhene, kupala kwapata bhene bhubhabhii leghelike. Nikitehi kila kilebhe kwa bhando bhoha kupala kwakombola kwa ndela jhojhoha jhela.
\p 
\v 23 Hengite ghanga ghoha kwa nhwalo gwa Lilobhe lya Mbone, na nenga mbate mota yake.
\v 24 Bho, umanya jhe bhando pa bhabhutuka, bhoha bhabhutuka, nambo jhola jwabhalongolela bhajhake ndi jwapata hupo? Mmutuke yenio mpate hupo.
\v 25 Mundo jhojhoha jwapala kwapeta bhajhake mukubhutuka, hote aghaleka ghoha, ahenga naha kupala apate hupo jhihangabhika! Nambo twenga tuhenga naha kwa nhwalo gwa kupata kilemba changahangabhika.
\v 26 Yene nibhutuka ngita mundo jhumbala kwalongolela, nikomana jhe ngita mundo akomana na upepo.
\v 27 Nambo ning'ahicha yegha jhango na kulongocha, nihenga yenio kupala pumbala kujhomolela kwatangachii bhando bhange ne namwete ngoto kukanilwa mukupoke hupo.
\c 10
\s1 Pauli ikanakiya kuijhinamii inyagho
\p 
\v 1 Makalongo bhango, nipala umanye kubhehe akahoko bhito bhatyangita kongo bhalongwichwa na lihunde, na bhoha bhajhakujhomboka njelembo mbwane ngele.
\v 2 Bhoha bhakabatichwe bhabhehe bha Mucha mulihunde lela na mumbwane.
\v 3 Bhoha bhalila chakulyegha chechelachela cha kiuhuke,
\v 4 helahela bhanywila chela cha kiuhuke, nhwalo bhakanywile kubhoke mulindalabho lya kiuhuke lilyakengima, lindalabho lyenio likibha Kilichitu jwenio.
\v 5 Nambo, bhando bhamahele bhahengita jhe ilebhe yaipala Chapanga, na mahele bhakawile na malelo ghabhe ghakapechingine kunjenga.
\p 
\v 6 Ngohe, mambu gheniya ghoha ndi nnandanikiho tugha kwito, ghatukelebhuwa kuhenga mabhoho ngita bheniya chibhahengita.
\v 7 Nkoto kuijhinamii inyagho ngita bhange chibhahengita, ngita Majhandiko chighalonge, “Bhando bhakatamite mukulye na kunywegha, bhajhakujhema na kukina kingongola.”
\v 8 Mwangatenda jhe ngongola, ngita bhange chibhatenda bhando bhange, lichiko limo bhando elufo ichilini na tato bhajhakukomolekelwa.
\v 9 Nkoto kunnyigha Bhambo Kilichitu ngita bhando bhange chibhanyighita, bhoha bhakawile kwa kulumwa na lijhoka!
\v 10 Nkotoka kukokoleka ngita bhando bhange chibhatehila, na bhene bhakakomilikilwa na ntumiche jwa kunane kwa Chapanga jwakoma!
\p 
\v 11 Bhahe, mambu gheniya ghakapitile kupala twenga tubholwe, ghakajhandikwe kwa nhwalo gwa kutukanikiya twenga kubhehe machiko ghabhandikii kujhomolela.
\p 
\v 12 Jwahambuka ajhemite nganganga, akilolekiye akotoka kugwegha!
\v 13 Majhighanikilo ghumpatite maghene jhe kwa bhando. Chapanga ndi jwahobholeka, jwenio anneka jhe mangota kupeta makakala ghino. Nambo pumujhighanikilwa, jwenio nampela makakala gha kuhimbalila na ndela jha kupitila.
\p 
\v 14 Kwa nhwalo gwenio, makalongo bhango bhunimpala, ntame kutale na kujhinamila inyagho.
\v 15 Nilonge na mangota ngita bhando bhina malango, uhwache mabhene gheniya ghinilongela.
\v 16 Putunnomba Chapanga kwa kikombe chela cha mota, bho, tubhehe jhe pamonga mu miyahe jha Kilichitu? Na putumetula libumunda, bho, tubhehe jhe pamonga muyegha jha Kilichitu?
\v 17 Nhwalo libumunda lyenio limo, na twenga bhitubhii twe ndi yegha jhimo, nhwalo bhoha tulye libumunda lyenio.
\p 
\v 18 Dolekeya bhando bha ku Ichilahele bhene, bhala bhubhalila litambiko bhilombana na kachangwale kupete matambiko gheniya.
\v 19 Ngohe nilonge nike? Kubhehe chakulyegha chikitambikilwe inyagho ndi kikolongwa kuliku chakulyegha? Bho, na inyagho yenio itangatila nike?
\v 20 Ng'oo! Chinilongela ndi chenje, litambiko lya bhando bhangaumanya Chapanga bhahipikiya michuka, nambo Chapanga jhe. Ne mbahijhe mangota mme maghumba nde na michuka.
\v 21 Mihotojhe kunywelekeya kikombi cha Bhambo na kongo mukinywelekeya kikombi cha michuka, mihoto ndeka kulye chakulyegha cha Bhambo na kongo mulye chakulya cha michuka.
\v 22 Bho, tupala Bhambo abhehe na wiho? Bho, miwacha tubhii na makakala kuliku jwenio?
\s1 Uhenge ghoha kwa ukolongwa gwa Chapanga
\p 
\v 23 Bhando bhange bhilonge, “Ilebhe yoha ikanikiwa ndeka,” nambo ne nilonge yoha yamaha jhe. Peniya bhange bhalonge, “Ilebhe yoha ikanikiwa ndeka,” nambo ne nilonge ilebhe yoha jhe ichenga.
\v 24 Mundo jhojhoha pakate jhino akotoka kupalaya ghambone gha kuntangatii jwenio, nambo apalaha gha mbone kwa nhwalo gwa ajhake.
\p 
\v 25 Yoha ichuluchwa mulighuliho lya nyama mihoto kulye changakonyakonya nhwalo gwa kuhengeleka umiojho.
\v 26 Nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge, “Nnema na ilebhe yoha ibhii nkate ndi ya Bhambo.”
\p 
\v 27 Anda mundo jwangannyeketela Kilichitu ankemangana mukalye kajhake, na mangota nnyeketile kujhenda.
\p Nnyakile chochoha kichibhekitwe palonge jhino changakukonyakonya kwa nhwalo gwa mwojho ghino.
\v 28 Nambo anda mundo jwannobholela mangota, “Chakulyegha chenje kitambikilwe inyagho,” mangalye jhe kwa nhwalo gwa jwenio jwannobholile na kwa nhwalo gwa mwojho.
\v 29 Nilonge, Kwa nhwalo gwa mwojho gwa jhonge. Mundo jhonge anda ankonyite, “Nhwalo gwa nike kukombolelwa kwango kuhadabulwe na mwojho gwa mundo jhonge?
\v 30 Anda ninchenguu Chapanga kwa chinilyegha, nhwalo gwa nike mundo jhonge alongele ghangana ndela kwa kilebhe chenie chinichenguu Chapanga?”
\p 
\v 31 Bhahe, chochoha chimuhenga, kibhehe ndi kulye na kunywegha, ntende ghoha kwa ung'alicho gwa Chapanga.
\v 32 Nkotoka kwatenda Akayahude amu kwa Akagilike amu kwa bhando bha Chapanga bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu bhakobondoke.
\v 33 Mme ngita nenga, ne nipala kwahalalicha bhando bhoha kwa ghoha ghunihenga. Nhwalo nikipalakii jhe ghambone namwete tugha, nambo nipalaha kwa nhwalo gwa bhando bhoha bhakombolelwe.
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Ungengame nenga ngita nenga chininkengama Kilichitu.
\s1 Kupuka muto pumunyinamii Chapanga
\p 
\v 2 Ninumbalila nhwalo minngomboka kwa kila kilebhe na kughakamula malaghalikilo ghunipekii.
\v 3 Nambo nipala kabhele mmanye kubhehe Kilichitu ndi muto gwa kila munalome, na munalome ndi muto gwa nhwana mundo, Chapanga ndi muto gwa Kilichitu.
\v 4 Bhahe, kila munalome jwannyinamila Chapanga amu jwatangacha lilobhe lya Chapanga kongo apukite muto gwake jwampela hone Kilichitu.
\v 5 Na mwikeghe jhojhoha pannyinamii Chapanga amu kutangacha malobhe gha Chapanga changapuka muto gwake, ampela hone munalome jwake, jwatehila naha tela tugha na mwikeghe jwachekwile majhunjo umuto.
\v 6 Mwikeghe jwangapukita muto gwake, mbaha achekule majhunjo ghake. Nambo anda ibhii hone kwa mwikeghe kuchekula amu kupungucha majhunjo ghake, bhahe, mbaha apuke muto gwake.
\v 7 Munalome yamaha jhe kupuka muto gwake, nhwalo jwenio ndi nnandanikiho gwa Chapanga na ung'alicho gwake Chapanga. Nambo mwikeghe ndi ung'alicho gwa munalome.
\v 8 Munalome apitii jhe kwa mwikeghe, nambo mwikeghe apitii kwa munalome.
\v 9 Munalome apanginwe jhe kwa nhwalo gwa mwikeghe, nambo mwikeghe apanganiwe kwa nhwalo gwa munalome.
\v 10 Ndi nhwalo mwikeghe ipuka muto gwake kubhehe ukindendeke ghubhii panane jhake na kwa akatumiche bha kunane kwa Chapanga.
\v 11 Helahela, palonge jha Bhambo mwikeghe akihobholela ndeka changa munalome, na jwenio munalome akihobholela ndeka changa mwikeghe.
\v 12 Anda hela mwikeghe chapitila kwa munalome, helahela munalome abhelwike na mwikeghe, nambo kila kilebhe kihuma kwa Chapanga.
\p 
\v 13 Nnyomole mabhene, bho, chambone mwikeghe kunnyinamii Chapanga kongo apukite jhe kilebhe chochoha umuto gwake?
\v 14 Chapanga papangina ilangii hotu munalome kubhehe na majhunjo mandandamaho ndi hone jhake,
\v 15 nambo kwa mwikeghe anda abhii na majhunjo mandandamaho, chenie ndi kilebhe chamaha kwa jwenio. Nhwalo apekilwe majhunjo mandandamaho ghampuke.
\v 16 Mundo anda ipala kutaungana pakate jha lijhambu lende, twenga tukwete jhe ghutuyobhalile ghange, hilu bhando bha Chapanga bhubhahobhalile Kilichitu bhakwete jhe ghabhayobhalila ghange.
\s1 Chakulyegha cha Bhambo
\r Matei 26:26-29; Maluku 14:22-25; Luka 22:14-20
\p 
\v 17 Mu malaghalikilo ghanga ghughahika ninombangana jhe, nhwalo mu makonganiko ghino gha kunnyinamii Chapanga mughatenda ghanganandela kuliku ghambone.
\v 18 Pukutumbulila, pumukonganika pamonga upitii mpechangano pakate jhino, na nenga pandina nilipala lijhambu lende.
\v 19 Ipalwa pabhehe na mpechangano pakate jhino, kupala bhala bhibhanyeketela Chapanga bhamanyikane.
\v 20 Pumukonganika pamonga, mihola miilye chakulya cha kunkomboka Bhambo kone nahi jhe!
\v 21 Nhwalo pakulyegha, kila mundo alyegha changa lendelela bhange, ade bhange bhabhehe na njala kone bhange bhalobhile!
\v 22 Bho, mihoto jhe kulye na kunywegha kajha kwino? Amu bho, mwapechelecha bhando bha Chapanga bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu na kwapeke hone bhene bhanga kilebhe? Ngohe ninobholele nike? Bho, ninombe? Ng'oo! Ninomba jhe kwa lijhambu lende.
\p 
\v 23 Nhwalo nenga mbokii kuhumii kwa Bhambo malaghalikilo ghunimpekii, Bhambo Yecho pajhambilwa uhiko ghola, ajhakutola libumunda,
\v 24 pajhomolila kunchenguu Chapanga, ajhakumetula, ajhakulonge, “Jhenjeno ndi yegha jhango jhunibhoha kwa nhwalo gwino mangota, ntende naha kwa kungomboka nenga.”
\v 25 Helahela pubhajhomolila kulyegha, ajhakutola kibaba, ajhakulonge: “Chenjeno ndi kibaba cha lilaghano liyono lya miyahe jhango. Ntende naha kila pumunywegha kwa kungomboka nenga.”
\p 
\v 26 Nhwalo kila mukulyegha libumunda na kunywela kibaba chenje, mutangacha kuwe kwa Bhambo, ade papalakuhika kabhele.
\v 27 Yene, mundo jhojhoha jwalyegha libumunda hele amu kuinywela kibaba jha Bhambo changatopela, jwenio chabhehe atei uhakaho kwa yegha na miyahe jha Bhambo.
\v 28 Bhahe, kila mundo akilolekiye jwenio, peniya ndi ahoto kulyegha libumunda lende na kunywela kibaba chenie.
\v 29 Nhwalo mundo jhojhoha jwalyegha na kunywegha abhehe na uchakaka ndi yegha jha Bhambo, changatenda yenio akiletela luhadabulo jwenio.
\v 30 Ndi mana bhando bhamahele pakate jhino bhaleghelike na bhange bhilwalwa, na bhange bhajhomwike.
\v 31 Anda tukihingukiye mbone, ngatuhadabwilwe jhe na Chapanga.
\v 32 Nambo putuhadabulwa na Bhambo, tubholwa kutama mbone, tukoto kuhadabulwa pamonga na bhando bhangaumanya Chapanga pannema.
\p 
\v 33 Kwa ghanga, makalongo bhango, pumukukonganika kulye chakulya cha Bhambo, kila jhumo annendelela nnyake.
\v 34 Mundo anda abhii na njala, alya kajhake, pumukonganika nkotoka kuhadabulwa na Chapanga. Nambo ghange, chinimmola pumbalakuhika.
\c 12
\s1 Itoi kuhumii kwa Uhuke gwa Chapanga
\p 
\v 1 Ngohe makalongo bhango,
\p nipala umanye mbone kwa malobhe gha itoi kuhumii kwa Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\v 2 Mmanye kubhehe, mmanyite jhe Chapanga, mukalongwichwe mundela yanganandela kuijhinamii inyagho yanga bhehe na ughome.
\v 3 Bhahe, nipala umanye kubhehe mundo jhojhoha jwalongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga ahoto kulonge, “Yecho alapanikile!” Helahela, abhii jhe mundo jhojhoha jwahoto kulonge, “Yecho ndi Bhambo,” pangalongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\p 
\v 4 Ibhii itoi yamahele, nambo Uhuke jwaibhoha ndi jhumo.
\v 5 Ibhii ndela yamahele mukunhengela, nambo Bhambo jwatunhengela ndi jhumo.
\v 6 Ibhii ndela yamahele mukuhenga lihengo, nambo Chapanga ndi jhumo jwenio jwahenga mahengo ghoha kwa bhando bhoha.
\v 7 Chapanga iyekulila kila mundo kwa kwatangatila bhando bhoha.
\v 8 Uhuke ampekii jhumo malobhe gha malango, na Uhuke jhojho ampekii jhonge uhotolo gwa kumanya ilebhe ngita champala jwenio Uhuke.
\v 9 Uhuke jhojho ampekii mundo kihobholelo, na Uhuke jhojho ampekii kitoi cha kwalamicha bhibhalwalwa,
\v 10 Uhuke gwa Chapanga ampekii jhonge uhotolo gwa kuhenga ikangacho, Uhuke jhojho ampekii jhonge uhotolo gwa kubhoha ulondole gwa Chapanga, na jhonge kulekanicha uhuke gwa Chapanga na yangabhehe ya Uhuke gwa Chapanga, jhonge alonge kwa lugha jhangamanyikana na jhonge kitoi cha kuchimulila chikilongelwa.
\v 11 Lyenio lyoha ndi lihengo lya Uhuke jwenio jhumo, na jwenio imaghulila kila mundo kitoi ngita chapala jwenio.
\s1 Yegha jhimo nambo ihungo yamahele
\p 
\v 12 Yegha ndi jhimo ipanginwe na ihungo yamahele, na pamonga ubhii na ilebhe yamahele, nambo ipangine yegha jhimo, yenio ndi chibhii kwa Kilichitu.
\v 13 Nhwalo twenga tubatichwe kwa Uhuke ghumo tubhehe yegha jhimo, tubhehe Akayahude amu bhangabhehe Akayahude, tubhehe twakabhanda amu twakabhanda jhe, bhoha tunywelichwe Uhuke jhojho jhumo.
\p 
\v 14 Yegha ipanginwe jhe na kihungo chimo, nambo ibhii ihungo yamahele.
\v 15 Lukongono anda lulongela, “Nhwalo nenga nalubhoko jhe, bhahe nenga jwa yegha jhe,” bho, lukongono lubhehe lwa yegha jhe? Nahi jhe!
\v 16 Anda lichikilo lilongile, “Nhwalo nenga jwa liho jhe, bhahe, nenga jwa yegha jhe,” bho, nhwalo lichikilo jwa yegha jhe? Nahi jhe!
\v 17 Anda yegha jhoha ngaibhehe liho, nganyohine bho? Anda yegha jhoha ngaibhehe lichikilo, ngatunuite bho?
\v 18 Nambo Chapanga abhekite kila ihungo kila chehemo mu yegha ngita chapahile.
\v 19 Ngita ihungo yoha anda ngakibhehe kihungo chimo, bho, yegha ngaibhii koo?
\v 20 Uchakaka ndi kubhehe, ibhii ihungo yamahele, nambo yegha ndi jhimo.
\p 
\v 21 Bhahe, liho lihoto ndeka kunnobholela lubhoko, “Nimpahi jhe mwe.” Hilu muto uhoto jhe kughalobholela makongono, “Ngwete malola na magholo.”
\v 22 Nambo kupeta gheniya, kubhehe ihungo yenio ya yegha ibhonekana kubhehe ileghelike, yenio ndi ipalwa hake.
\v 23 Kabhele ihungo hela tulonge kubhehe yanganandela, ndi ibhekwa mbone hake, na ihungo ibhonekana yambone jhe tuighubikila mbone.
\v 24 Nambo ihungo ibhonekana yambone hake, ipalwa jhe kulolekewa mbone. Chapanga jwenio abhekite yenio yegha, na chikipela utopaho chela chikiponokiwa,
\v 25 kupala kwangabhehe jhe na mpechangano payegha, nambo ipagwa yoha itangatilane.
\v 26 Anda kihungo chimo kilwalwa, bhahe, ipagwa yoha ilwalwa pamonga na chenie, anda kihungo chimo kilombwitwe, ihungo yoha ihangana pamonga na chenie.
\p 
\v 27 Bhahe, mangota mabhoha ndi yegha jha Kilichitu, kila jhumo ndi kihungo cha yegha jhenie.
\v 28 Mu lilongo lya bhando bhubhajheketii Kilichitu, hote Chapanga abhekite akatenga na jwa ubhele milondole bha Chapanga na jwa utato bhabhola na jwa ncheche bhala bhubhatenda ikangacho, bhala bhubhapekiwe makakala gha kwalamicha bhibhalwalwa, na bhubhahoto kwatangatii bhando bhange, peniya ilongoche na bhubhalonge lugha jhangamanyikana.
\v 29 Bho, bhando bhoha ndi akatenga? Bho, bhando bhoha ndi milondole bha Chapanga? Bho, bhando bhoha ndi bhabhola? Bho, bhando bhoha bhakwete kitoi cha kuhenga ikangacho?
\v 30 Bho, bhando bhoha bhakwete kitoi cha kulamicha bhando? Bho, bhando bhoha bhakwete kitoi cha kulonge lugha jhangamanyikana? Bho, bhoha bhichimulila lugha jhibhalongela?
\v 31 Yene mwipale hake itoi ibhii ikolongwa.
\p Na nenga ngohe chaninangiya ndela jha mbone hake kupeta yoha.
\c 13
\s1 Mapalano
\p 
\v 1 Pange nongele lugha jha bhando na lugha jha akatumiche bha kunane kwa Chapanga, nambo anda ngwete jhe upalo, bhahe, nenga nanandana na lipenenga lililela jhajhe amu nalingengecha.
\v 2 Pange nkwete kitoi chukutangacha lilobhe lya Chapanga, na kumanya chile yoha na kumanya kila kilebhe, anda ngwete kihobholelo cha kubhoha itombe, nambo anda ngwete jhe upalo ne kilebhe nacho.
\v 3 Anda pange napekii akahocho ilebhe yango yoha nu kuibheka yegha jhango m umwotu itinike, nambo anda ngwete jhe upalo ne kilebhe nacho.
\p 
\v 4 Mundo jwabhii na upalo uhimbilila, na ubhehe na kiya, akwete jhe wiho, akitondobhehe jhe hilu kuloka.
\v 5 Mundo jhuna upalo utembekeya, akipalakii jhe yambone yake jwenio, hilu ajhojhoke jhe mulilaka, aghabheka jhe ghanganandela mumwojho,
\v 6 mundo jhuna upalo ahanganii jhe ghangana ndela, nambo ahanganila gha ukwele.
\v 7 Mundo jhuna upalo ahimbalila yoha, ujheketela ghoha, uhobholela ghoha na ulepelela jhe na lyolyoha.
\p 
\v 8 Upalo ujhomoka jhe. Anda kibhii kitoi cha ulondole gwa Chapanga chakijhomokela, anda kibhii kitoi cha kulonge kwa lugha jhangamanyikana, chenio nakujhomokela, anda kibhii kitoi cha kumanya, na chenie nakipeta.
\v 9 Nhwalo kumanya kwito na kupiya kwito ulondole gwa Chapanga kupongwike.
\v 10 Nambo chela chikitwelile pikipala kuhika, chela kipengwa nakihobholela.
\p 
\v 11 Punikibha mwana king'enya, nongila ngita mwana, nikamanyite ngita mwana, nikawachii ngita mwana. Nambo pungolita nikaghalekite ghoha ghauhwana.
\v 12 Chitukibhona ngohe ndi ngita kulolekeya mu lindala lela changabhonekana maha, nambo palonge natulola miho kwa miho. Nambo ngohe nimanya pandina tugha, peniya palonge chamanya ghoha ngita chighapalwa, ngita Chapanga chamanya nenga.
\p 
\v 13 Ngohe ghatamakii mambu ghanga matato, kihobholelo na lihobholelo na upalo, nambo kilebhe kikolongwa kupeta ghoha ndi upalo.
\c 14
\s1 Mabholo ghukujhojhekeya gha Uhuke gwa Chapanga
\p 
\v 1 Nkengame upalo. Nambo jha kuchocha itoi ya kumwojho ya Uhuke gwa Chapanga, ngolongwa ndi kupiya ulondole gwa Chapanga.
\v 2 Mundo jwalonge lugha yangamanyikana, jwenio alongii jhe na bhando nambo alonge na Chapanga, nhwalo abhii jhe mundo jwamanya chalongela, alonge mambu ghighahitwe kwa likakala lya Uhuke gwa Chapanga.
\v 3 Nambo jhola jwapiya ulondole gwa Chapanga gwa kutangacha lilobhe lya Chapanga, ilonge na bhando na kwatangatila, kwa abhaleke na kwapepecha miojho.
\v 4 Jwalongela lugha jhangamanyikana, akichenga jwenio, nambo jhola jwapiya ulondole gwa Chapanga, abhakangamalicha bhando bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 5 Bhahe, nenga ngambahi mangota mabhoha nnongele kwa lugha jhangamanyikana, nambo chikipala hake ndi kupiya ulondole gwa kutangacha lilobhe lya Chapanga. Nhwalo mundo jhola jwapiya ulondole gwa lilobhe lya Chapanga ihenga ghambone kuliku jhola jwapiya ulondole gwa kulonge lugha jhangamanyikana, nambo anda abhii mundo jhonge jwahoto kuchimulila lugha jhangamanyikana kwa bhando bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu ahoto kwatangatila.
\v 6 Ngohe makalongo bhango, anda hikite kwino nu kulonge na mangota kwa lugha jhangamanyikana, bho, nanyambulila nike? Chakaka nanyambulila jhe kilebhe! Nanyambulila anda nilonge na mangota kwa uyekulilo gwa Chapanga amu kumanya amu Lilobhe lya ulondole gwa Chapanga amu mabholo.
\p 
\v 7 Anda ilebhe yangabhehe na ughome na ibhoha lilobhe, ngita kitolilo na lilimba. Bho, mundo naumanya bhole nhwambo ghuhonwa anda yombo yenio ibhoha lilobhe lyangamanyikana?
\v 8 Ngita lipenenga libhoha ndeka lilobhe lyamaha, ghane jwakilenganikiye kujhenda kungondo?
\v 9 Helahela mangota, anda ghimulongela ghamanyikana ndeka, ghane nahotola bhole kumanya? Yene namma anda ilalama jhajhe.
\v 10 Ibhii lugha mbwe pannema, nambo yoha ileta mana.
\v 11 Nambo anda nenga nimanyite jhe chilonge mundo jhonge, nenga nibhehe naghene kwa mundo jwenio jhuilongela na nenga, na jwenio abhehe nng'ene kwa nenga.
\v 12 Helahela mangota mabhoha, nhwalo mipala hake kupokela itoi ya Uhuke gwa Chapanga, nkangamale kujhonjekeya itoi itenda bhando bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu bhakangamale.
\p 
\v 13 Mundo jhola jwalongela kwa lugha ngene, annyope Chapanga kitoi chakuhoto kwachimulila bhando chela chalongela.
\v 14 Nhwalo, anda nyopite kwa lugha ngene, uhuke jhango ndi ghunyopa Chapanga, nambo malango ghango ghahenga ndeka kilebhe.
\v 15 Ngohe ndenda bhole? Chanyopa kwa uhuke gwango, helahela chanyopa kwa malango ghango, chanyemba kwa uhuke gwango helehela chanyemba kwa malango ghango.
\v 16 Anda munnombalila Chapanga gwino kwa uhuke gwino tugha, anda abhii pakate jhino mundo jwangamanya chimulongela, nahotola bhole kukung'ila “Amina,” pumunchenguu Chapanga anda amanyiti chimulongela?
\v 17 Nahotola kunnomba Chapanga mbone, nambo jhola nakintangatila jhe kilebhe.
\p 
\v 18 Ninnomba Chapanga nhwalo nenga nilongela lugha ngene kuliku mangota mabhoha.
\v 19 Nambo kwa lilongo lya bhando bhubhajheketii Kilichitu ngambaii kulonge malobhe nhwano ghighamanyikana, kwabhola bhando bhange kuliku kulonge malobhe ghamahele kwa lugha ngene.
\p 
\v 20 Makalongo bhango, nkotoka kuwacha ngita yana ichokombe nambo mubhoho mme anda yana ichokombe, pumuwacha mme ngita bhando akanahota.
\v 21 Ijhandikwe mu Malaghalikilo, “Bhambo alonge naha,
\q1 ‘Kwa ndela jha bhubhalonge lugha ngene,
\q1 nanongela na bhando bhango alonge Bhambo,
\q1 na kwa nnomo gwa akaghene,
\q1 chanongela na bhando bheniya, pamonga yenio nabhajhoha jhe.’ ”
\m 
\v 22 Ngohe bhahe, kulonge lugha ngene, ndi nginyililo kwa bhando bhangajheketela, nambo chi kwa bhala bhubhajheketela Kilichitu. Nambo kupiya ulondole gwa Chapanga kwa nhwalo gwa bhala bhubhajheketii nambo kwa bhala bhangajheketela.
\p 
\v 23 Bhahe, lilongo lya bhando bhoha bhubhajheketii Kilichitu pubhakonganika pamonga, na kila jhumo kutumbuu kulonge kwa lugha ngene, bhala bhangajheketela na bhangamanya kilebhe anda bhahikite, bho, nabhahola jhe kulonge mangota nkwete ngholoka?
\v 24 Nambo bhoha bhubhapiya ulondole gwa Chapanga, bhando bhangajheketela na bhangamanya kilebhe anda bhahikite, nabhajhoha ghoha ghumulongela nabhamanya uhakaho gwabhe, na nabhahadabulwa na bhoha.
\v 25 Na ilebhe yoha ihibhililwe miyojho jhabhe naibhaha pakongoloho, na bhene chatama makilikite na kunnyinamila Chapanga kone nabhalongela, “Chakaka Chapanga abhii pamonga na mangota.”
\s1 Kilebhe ghane kihengeke mulilongo lya bhando bhubhajheketii Kilichitu
\p 
\v 26 Makalongo bhango, ngohe tulongele nike? Pumukonganika pamo kunnyinamii Chapanga, jhumo ajhemba nhwambo, na jhonge abhole, na jhonge abhehe na uloto kuhumii kwa Chapanga, na jhonge alongela lugha ngene na jhonge achimulila ghighalongelwa. Ghoha ghahengeke kwa nhwalo gwa kwatangatila lilongo lya bhando bhubhajheketii Kilichitu.
\v 27 Anda bhabhii bhando bhakulonge lugha ngene, bhabhele amu bhatato bhalongela, nambo alonge jhumo jhumo, na kongo abhii mundo jhonge jwa kwachimulila chikilongelwa.
\v 28 Nambo anda abhii jhe mundo jwa kwachimulila chikilongelwa, bhahe, mundo jhola jwalongela lugha ngene atame nuu mulilongo lya bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu, alonge mumwojho gwake na Chapanga.
\v 29 Bhando bhabhele amu bhatato bhubhatangacha Malobhe gha Chapanga, bhahoto kulonge bhabhele amu bhatato, bhange bhakoto kuhadabula malobhe ghala ghighalongelwa.
\v 30 Anda abhii mundo mulilongo lyenio jwapokii Malobhe gha Chapanga, bhahe, jhola jwalongela atame nuu.
\v 31 Nhwalo mangota mabhoha mihoto kupiya ulondole gwa Chapanga jhumo jhumo, kila mundo akibhola na akangamalichwe mwojho.
\v 32 Ihuke ya milondole bha Chapanga ijhoha milondole bha Chapanga.
\v 33 Nhwalo Chapanga chi Chapanga jwakuhenga ilebhe ya bhulo, nambo jwenio ndi Chapanga jwa uteeke.
\p Helahela anda mulilongo lya bhando lilinyeketii Kilichitu,
\v 34 akakeghe bhatame nuu mu malilongo gha bhando ghighannyeketii Kilichitu, bhakotoka kulonge, hilu kulongocha anda lilaghalikilo chililongela.
\v 35 Anda bhapala kunkonya, bhankonye akangana bhabhe kajhabhe, nhwalo hone kwa mwikeghe kulonge chochoha palilongo lya bhando lilinyeketii Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 36 Bho, miwacha Lilobhe lya Chapanga lihumita kwino amu lihikite kwa mangota kanjika tugha?
\v 37 Anda mundo jhojhoha awacha kubhehe apekiwe Malobhe gha Chapanga, amu kitoi chenge cha Uhuke gwa Chapanga, amanye kubhehe ghanga ghinijhandika ndi nhwilo gwa Bhambo.
\v 38 Nambo mundo aghapucha ghanga, bhahe, nkoto kunholela mundo jwenio.
\p 
\v 39 Bhahe, makalongo bhango, mme na unoghe hake kupiya ulondole gwa Chapanga, nambo nkotoka kwakanakiya bhando kulonge kwa lugha ngene.
\v 40 Nambo ghoha ghahengeka mbone kila kilebhe ngita chiipalwa.
\c 15
\s1 Kuyoka kwa Kilichitu
\p 
\v 1 Ngohe makalongo bhango, mbala kunkombocha Malobhe gha Mbone ghunintangachila, ghimpokii na kubhehe nchinge gwa kuhobholela kwino, na kwa gheniya mangota nnyemite nganganga.
\v 2 Lilobhe lyenio linintangachii ndi Lilobhe lya Mbone, mangota nang'ombokoka anda mughakamwii maha ghala ghunintangachila, anda nahi jhe bhahe, kuhobholela kwino jhajhe.
\p 
\v 3 Nenga nikampekii mangota ghala ghimbokii nenga namwete, kubhehe Kilichitu awile kwa nhwalo gwa uhakaho gwito ngita chighalonge Majhandiko gha Chapanga,
\v 4 kubhehe awile na kuyoka lichiko lya utato ngita chighalonge Majhandiko gha Chapanga.
\v 5 Akatumbwii kumpitii Kefa, kabhele ajhakwapitila akatenga kome na bhabhele.
\v 6 Helahela ajhakwapitila akalongo mamiya nhwano kwa mala jhimo, bhamahele bhabhii ghome, nambo bhange bhajhomwike.
\v 7 Paligha ajhakumpitila Yakobu, na peniya ajhakwapitila akatenga bhoha.
\p 
\v 8 Kujhomolela kwake ajhakumbitii nenga, ngita mundo jhumelwikwe changatimicha miyehe jhango.
\v 9 Nhwalo nenga ndi natenga jwandina pakate jha akatenga bhoha, nitope jhe kukemwa natenga, nhwalo nakaghang'ahite makunde gha bhando ghighanyeketii Kilichitu.
\v 10 Nambo, kwa umbone gwa Chapanga, undei mme ngita chimile, na umbone gwake ukibha jhajhe jhe. Nenga hengite lihengo kupete akatenga bhoha, ne jhe, nambo umbone gwa Chapanga uhengita lihengo pamonga na nenga.
\v 11 Kwa nhwalo gwenio, ibhehe nenga amu bheniya bhubhatangacha Malobhe gha Mbone kilebhe jhe, chenje ndi twatangachila bhando na chenje ndi chitujheketela.
\s1 Kuyoka kwa bhando
\p 
\v 12 Ngohe, nhwalo itangachwa kubhehe Kilichitu ayokite kubhoke mu kuwegha, bho, nhwalo ghane bhange bhilonge kubhii jhe kuyoka?
\v 13 Anda kubhii jhe kuyoka kwa bhando, bhahe, Kilichitu na jwenio ayokite jhe,
\v 14 anda Kilichitu ayokite jhe, bhahe, chituntangacha kilebhe nacho, helahela kihobholelo chino kilebhe nacho.
\v 15 Kupeta gheniya, helahela twenga tubhonekana tulongii uwange panane jha Chapanga, kwa nhwalo tulongii Chapanga akayokiche Kilichitu, chakaka akayokiche jhe, ngita hela bhubhawile bhahyokichwa jhe.
\v 16 Nhwalo ikibha chakaka kubhehe bhubhawile kuyoka jhe, bhahe na jwenio Kilichitu ayokite jhe.
\v 17 Anda Kilichitu ayokite jhe, bhahe, kihobholelo chino kilebhe nacho, na mwamela muhakaho gwino.
\v 18 Helahela bhando bhubhawile kone bhannyeketii Kilichitu bhahobhalile.
\v 19 Anda tuhobhalila Yecho Kilichitu muughome ghongo tugha, twenga tupalwa kubhonelwa kiya kuliku bhando bhoha pannema.
\p 
\v 20 Nambo uchakaka ndi kubhehe Kilichitu ahyokichwe kuhumii muweghe, jwenio ndi jwatumbulila kuyoka pakate jha bhando bhubhagholwike mukuwegha.
\v 21 Anda kuwegha kuletitwa na mundo jhumo, helahela kuyoka kubhoke muweghe na kwenie kuletitwa na mundo jhumo.
\v 22 Kwa nhwalo bhando bhoha bhiwegha kwa kulombana na Adamo, helahela kwa kulombana na Kilichitu bhando bhoha bhabhehe ghome.
\v 23 Nambo kila jhumo chayoka mu kipinde chake, kutumbulii Kilichitu, peniya bhala bhubhabhii bhake Kilichitu papakuhika.
\v 24 Peniya, kujhomolela nakuhika, Kilichitu papakumpe Chapanga Tate unahota nkolongwa, pajhomolela kuhangabhana ulongoche na ukindendeke na makakala ghoha ghanganandela.
\v 25 Nhwalo Kilichitu apalwa kulongocha ade Chapanga pahotola kwabula akamakoko bhoha na kwabheka pahe jha makongono ghake.
\v 26 Likoko lya kujhomolela jwapala kukomolekelwa ndi kuwegha.
\v 27 Nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge, “Chapanga abhekite ilebhe yoha pahe jha makongono ghake.” Nambo, Majhandiko pighalonge, “Ilebhe yoha ibhekitwe pahe jha makongono gha ilongoche,” chakaka kubhehe Chapanga abhii jhe muilebhe yenio, nhwalo jwenio Chapanga ndi jwaibheka ilebhe yoha pahe jha ukindendeke gwa Kilichitu na ahoto jhe kubhehe pahe jha Kilichitu.
\v 28 Nambo papala kubheka pahe jha ulongoche gwa Kilichitu, na jwenio Mwana chatama pahe jha ulongoche gwa Chapanga, jwabhekite yoha pahe jha ulongoche gwake, nhwalo Chapanga ilongocha yoha kila chehemo.
\p 
\v 29 Ngohe anda kuyoka kubhii jhe, bho, bhando bhala bhubhatichwa kwa nhwalo gwa bhubhawile nabhatenda bho? Anda bhubhawile bhayokichwa jhe, nhwalo ghane bhando bhibatichwa kwa nhwalo gwabhe?
\v 30 Nhwalo ghane na twenga tukibheka ngenyangenya jha ngondo kila lichaa?
\v 31 Makalongo bhango, machiko naghabhaha mukuhandahanda jha ngondo jha kuwegha! Nikiloka kwa nhwalo gwino mu kulombana na Yecho Kilichitu Bhambo gwito, ghindenda nnonge ghanga.
\v 32 Bho, nganyambulile kilebhe ghane pangomina na bhando bhubhalandine na inyama ijhoghowa kwenio ku Epecho? Nambo anda bhando bhubhawile nabhahyokichwa jhe bhahe, “Tulye na tunyweghe, nhwalo kilabho natuhwa.”
\p 
\v 33 Nkotoka kukopokelwa, “Ukoche gwanganandela uhangabhana luhomo lwambone.”
\v 34 Ngohe ung'ang'anuke! Nkoto kutenda uhakaho, nhwalo bhando bhange pakate jhino chakaka bhammanyite jhe Chapanga. Nilonge mambu ghanga nkola hone!
\s1 Yegha jha kuyoka
\p 
\v 35 Nambo mundo ahotola kukonya, “Bho, bhubhawile bhayoka bhole? Bho, chibhabha na yegha ghane?”
\v 36 Ngonyelo jhene jha kimbebhebhe! Mbejho yumichite imela jhe ade ihwe hote.
\v 37 Paumichita, umicha mbejho tugha, ibhe ya ngano amu mbejho henge, umicha jhe mmea ghupitila.
\v 38 Chapanga haipela mbejho liumbo lyalipala jwenio, kila mbejho libhehe na liumbo lya kanjika chake.
\p 
\v 39 Yegha ihumbi yoha ilandine jhe. Bhando bhakwete yegha jhabhe na inyama ikwete yegha yabhe, ijhune ikwete yegha yabhe na helahela homba ikwete yegha yabhe.
\p 
\v 40 Kabhele yegha ya kunane kwa Chapanga na yegha ya pannema, uwalanao gwa yegha ya kunane kwa Chapanga ilandinejhe na uwalanao yegha ya pannema.
\v 41 Lyobha libhii lya mbone na lubhalamwehe lubhii lwa uwalanaho na ndondwa ibhii na uhwalanaho gwake, na ndondwa yenio ilandinejhe muhwalanao.
\p 
\v 42 Yene ndi chipala kubhehe bhando pubhapala kuyokichwa kwa bhando bhubhawile. Yegha uchikwa kone ubholite, nambo uyoka changahangabhika.
\v 43 Uchikwa muhone, uhyokechwa muukolo, uchikwa kone uleghelike, uyokichwa mumakakala.
\v 44 Pauchikwa, uchikwa anda yegha jha umundo, peniya uyoka yegha jha kiuhuke. Anda ibhii yegha jha kiumundo, helahela ibhii yegha jha kiuhuke.
\v 45 Nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghalongela, “Mundo jwa kutumbula, Adamo, akibha mundo ghome,” nambo Adamo jwa kujhomolela ndi Uhuke gwa Chapanga jwabhapekea bhando ughome.
\v 46 Yegha jha kiuhukejhe jhilongolile, nambo yegha jha kiumundo ndi ulongolile, peniya ijhakuhika yegha jha kiuhuke.
\v 47 Mundo jwakutumbulila akapanginwe kuhumii mulutukunda lwa nnema, nambo mundo jhubhele abhokite kunane kwa Chapanga.
\v 48 Bhando bha pannema bhalandine na bhala bhapanginwe kwa undope, na bhala bhahumita kunane kwa Chapanga ndibhahumite kunane kwa Chapanga.
\v 49 Anda yenio chitulandine na jhola jwapanginwe kwa undope, helahela chatulandine na jhola jwahumita kunane kwa Chapanga.
\p 
\v 50 Bhahe akalongo bhango chinilongela ndi chenje, chela chikipanginwe kwa yegha na miyahe kihotolajhe kubhujhila unahota nkolongwa gwa Chapanga, hilu chela chikihangabhika kihotolajhe kuleka kuhangabhika.
\p 
\v 51 Nyokanikihe, ninobholele chile, bhoha natujhomoka ndeka, nambo bhoha natughalambulwa.
\v 52 Chwechwele kuchichila na kuhumbula anda liho pulikopekopela. Nhwalo lipenenga la kujhomolela pilipala kulela, bhubhawile chibhayokichwe kone yegha jhabhe ibholitejhe, peniya na twenga natuwejhe, nambo natughalambulwa.
\v 53 Nhwalo yegha jhihangabhika ipalwa ughalambuke kubhehe gwangahangabhika, yegha jhiwegha ighalambuke kubhehe jhangawegha.
\v 54 Bhahe, yegha jhenje jhihangabhika puighalambuka ikoto kuhangabhika, na chela chikibhii mukuwegha pakighalambuka kikoto kuwegha, peniya ndi chilitimile Lilobhe lya Chapanga lililongela, “Kuwegha kukomalikilwe, kituhotojhe kabhele!”
\q1 
\v 55 “Mwe kuwegha, bho, kuhoto kwino kubhii ko?
\q1 Mwe kuwegha bho, lipyanda lino libhii ko?”
\m 
\v 56 Kuwegha kubhehe na likakala nhwalo gwa uhakaho, na uhakaho libhehe na makakala nhwalo gwa lilaghalikilo.
\v 57 Nambo tunchenguu Chapanga jwatupekii likakala kupetela Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 58 Bhahe akalongo bhango, nnyemengane nganganga changa nyukunyuka. Machiko ghoha nnyendelele kuhenga lihengo lya Bhambo, nhwalo umanya kubhehe lihengo lino kwa kuntumikii Bhambo lya jhajhe jhe.
\c 16
\s1 Nchango gwa kwatangatii bhando bhubhajheketii Kilichitu
\p 
\v 1 Ngohe, nilongele malobhe gha kwachangii bhando bha Chapanga, ntende chenie ngita chinililobholile kwa lilongo lya bhando lilinyeketii Kilichitu lya ku Galatiya.
\v 2 Kila jumapile, kila mundo pakate jhino abheke mbijha yabhii nako, peniya abheke kihukilo nhwalo pambala kuhika kukoto kubhehe na nchango kabhele.
\v 3 Peniya pumbala kuhika kwino, nanatuma bhala bhimahagwile pakate jhino bhapeleke nchango na baluwa ku Yeluchalemo.
\v 4 Anda tela na nenga kujhenda kwenio, natulongohana pamonga.
\s1 Mambu ghapala kuhenga Pauli
\p 
\v 5 Pumbala kupeta kujhenda ku Makedoniya, hote natumbula kuhika kwino, nhwalo mbala kujhenda ku Makedoniya.
\v 6 Pange nihoto kutama na mangota pandina, amu kutama na mangota mu machiko ghoha gha malile, nhwalo undangatile mumwanja gwango kokoha kunijhenda.
\v 7 Nipala ndeka kukongana na mangota kwa kupeta tugha, mbala ndame na mangota pandina anda Bhambo apahile.
\p 
\v 8 Nambo chandama pamba ku Epecho ade lichiko lya Pendekochite,
\v 9 nhwalo nnyango gwango ubhii gwampala kwa lihengo lyango likolongwa pamba, anda bhabhii bhando bhamahele bhubhakana ghunilongela.
\p 
\v 10 Timocheyo anda ahika kwino, nkotoka kuntenda ajhoghope patama na mangota, nhwalo jwenio ahenga lihengo lya Bhambo ngita nenga.
\v 11 Yene mundo jhojhoha nkotoka kupucha, nambo mutangatile ajhendelele tela na mwanja gwake kwa nhwalo ahotole kubhujha kabhele kwa nenga, nhwalo ninendelela abhujhe na bhando bhango.
\p 
\v 12 Ngohe nongele malobhe gha nnongo gwito Apolu, nde kumpembelekeya ahike kwino pamonga na akalongo bhange, nambo apala jhe kuhika ngoheno, nambo chahika papata pwache.
\s1 Malobhe gha kujhomolela
\p 
\v 13 Nkeluwe, ntamangane maha mu kihobholelo chino, nkangamale mme na makakala.
\v 14 Kila kilebhe chimukihenga kihengwa kwa upalo.
\p 
\v 15 Makalongo bhango mmanye Sitefano na bhando bha kajha jhake, bheniya ndi bhando bhubhakatumbwii kupokela kihobholelo cha Kilichitu ku kilambo cha ku Akaya, peniya bhakipihite bhene kwa kwahengela bhando bha Chapanga. Yene makalongo bhango nimpembelekeya,
\v 16 mwajhokanikiye bhando ngita bheniya, na kila mundo ahenga lihengo pamonga nabho.
\p 
\v 17 Nihanganila hake pubhahikita Sitefano na Fotunato na Akaiko, nhwalo pubhakibha pamba tela na mangota kubhehe pamba.
\v 18 Nhwalo bhauhanganiche uhuke gwango ngita chinihanganiche mangota. Kwa nhwalo gwenio ipalwa kwakomboka bhando ngita bheniya.
\p 
\v 19 Bhando bhoha bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu bha ku Asiya bhanyambucha. Akula na Pilisila pamonga na likunde lya bhando bhoha bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu bhubhakonganika kujhopa kajhango bhanyambucha kwa liina lya Bhambo.
\v 20 Makalongo bhoha bhubhabhii pamba bhinyambucha.
\p Na mangota nnyambuchane mabhene kwa mabhene kulangii upalo gwa Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 21 Nenga Napauli ninyambucha, kongo ninyandikila ujhambucho ghongo kwa lubhoko lwango namwete.
\p 
\v 22 Mundo jhojhoha jwangampala Bhambo.
\p jwenio akilapanikii MARA NATHA. Bhambo gwito ahika!
\p 
\v 23 Umbone gwa Bhambo Yecho Kilichitu ubhaha pamo na mangota.
\p 
\v 24 Upalo gwango utame na mangota mabhoha bhunombine na Kilichitu Yecho.
